{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"40290-busy-ants","title":"Semut yang Sibuk","description":"Ikuti semut-semut di cerita ini. Mereka akan membuat pembaca kecil sibuk.","language":"Bahasa Indonesia","langCode":"id","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Nasema Zeerak"],"illustrators":["Deepa Balsavar"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"The Asia Foundation","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/40290-busy-ants"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/704670/size3/241eb27666dc624a6d0b5f5b2871e868.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/704670/size6/241eb27666dc624a6d0b5f5b2871e868.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13074/size6/6fdb6384a32650b9a5c3fa18e2911571.jpg","text":"Halo, aku semut keempat dalam barisan. Kamu lihat aku?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13075/size6/5a69c82d463c123769b132250d52614e.jpg","text":"Kiri, kanan, kiri, kanan. Kami berbaris tanpa suara.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13076/size6/d76a595d6193d51826a7f7fc650ed77a.jpg","text":"Aku punya ide. Aku akan naik sepatu roda supaya lebih cepat.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13077/size6/7534de2d1ce6d49e268aab3236a1920e.jpg","text":"Kami tidak berisik seperti binatang lain. Kami bicara dengan penciuman kami.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13078/size6/c1346b41f03c604b61cc7919576135f7.jpg","text":"Aroma sedap bilang, \"Ikuti aku. Ada makanan enak.\"","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13079/size6/16a843e35736981d828a9e6427f6ccc6.jpg","text":"Bau lain berkata, \"Bahaya! Jangan pergi ke sana.\"","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13080/size6/830248e8b11e9e7916ec154f0df68215.jpg","text":"Aku suka kue dan semua yang manis, sama seperti kamu.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13081/size6/8745c7edb8e0008518f0a4f305717985.jpg","text":"Mau lihat kekuatanku? Aku memang terlihat mungil, tapi aku sangat kuat.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13082/size6/2d6959400605bcf6866869e09e411f4b.jpg","text":"Meskipun pintu tertutup, aku bisa menyelinap lewat celah paling kecil.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13083/size6/ffca370f5d6841d1b40319e71feaa4b8.jpg","text":"Percaya atau tidak, kami hidup berbahagia dalam kelompok.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13084/size6/2a921d6470d9372bd2697500681c4558.jpg","text":"AYO KITA BELAJAR KATA-KATA BARU.\nKecil - Besar\nLambat - Cepat\nPendek - Tinggi\nKurus - Gemuk\nKeras - Lembut\nBerisik - Sepi\nItulah beberapa lawan kata. Bisakah kamu membuat kalimat dari masing-masing pasangan kata tersebut? Contohnya, 'Semut kecil; gajah besar'. \"Sibuk seperti semut\" adalah sebutan yang bagus untuk orang yang suka bekerja keras.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":148}}